➜双语漫画，11条小道理
http://www.sohu.com/a/426217765_100171577	16366
<p>一个人的世界观、人生观和价值观如何，将会决定他如何看待世界，如何看待生命，以及如何面对物质生活。</p>
<p>而三观的树立往往是每个人一生都在学习的过程。在孩提阶段，我们模仿大人的言行，接受教育，然后慢慢形成自己的理解和认知。在这个过程，许多道理与现实的矛盾可能会让孩子产生困惑。</p>
<p>以下这11条小道理，希望可以帮助爸爸妈妈们给孩子一个好的答案和指引……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>— 01 — 面对成功</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201021/abb9e7c55121494cb2b59e0db0c3f67c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>Being successful means </p>
<p>something different to each person</p>
<p>不要让别人告诉你什么是成功，</p>
<p>不要让别人帮你下成功的定义。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>— 02 — 对待梦想</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201021/f330240b3b24461694540ad843f0aa6e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">It's good to have big hopes and expectations</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">but keep them logical</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有野心和梦想总没错，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但也要懂得脚踏实地。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>— 03 — 面对未来</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201021/0daae874810d48ae85bd4b4253813060.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">Being normal is probably the lamest thing you can try to be</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没有什么事情比成为一个平庸的人更糟的了。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>— 04 — 面对恐惧</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201021/90cdd7222bb74fc886cf224c2c782af3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">You can't get to rid of your fear...</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">but you can learn to live with them</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你可能无法战胜恐惧，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但你可以试着和他们和平共处。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>— 05 — 选择环境和朋友</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201021/8c156b2e5f5f40fb9a6fb7566ecaf7af.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">Surround youeself with things and people that inspire you</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">选择那些可以给你带来正能量的人和事。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>— 06 — 面对孤独</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201021/0a18d12146974b4eb58106414b505b53.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">"Hello" is the most powerful word against loneliness</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当你孤独的时候，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">试着主动跟人打招呼。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>— 07 — 对待他人</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201021/8082549e307f4391b4b8cfe07079f7f8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">Don't push your friends into your stuff...</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">Let them find it and like it if they want to </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不要强迫你的朋友爱你所爱，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">除非他们自己愿意。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>— 08 — 面对不同</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201021/50a747ba21dd416a8d0758266d9f61b4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">you are not as weird as you think you are...</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">everyone feels a little than the rest.</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你没有你想象中的那么的奇怪，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其实每一个人或多或少都有不同于别人的地方。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>— 09 — 包容他人</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201021/502e3e2f8b244195ac24230c41307d57.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">There will always be prettier and uglier people than you.</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这个世界上，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">多得是比你丑和比你美的人。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">接受它并继续前行。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>— 10 — 真正的朋友</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201021/c334c894514b458dad5ca9130663c788.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">People who only call you when they need</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">something aren't upir friends.</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只在需要时想起你的人不能称作真正的朋友。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>— 11 — 保持好奇</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201021/5b414c6aea12451884cff465da0dd1fe.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>Stay open to new things.</p>
<p>保持好奇心。</p>
<p>人生很长，怎样才算过好了一生</p>
<p>告诉孩子：<strong>去体验、学习、收获</strong></p>
<p><strong>然后找到自己</strong></p>